The Terms-of-Service is based on that the user does not abuse this program in any malicious way or fashion

1. The Program/bot, hereafter refered to as "Software" is meant to help people. using it for any other purposes then what it is intended for will immediately violate the right to use it.

1.1 The Definition of "meant to help people" is in relation towards solving problems, such as someone having issues with their computer, or learning how to fix a problem they are generally having. The Software has a limited predefined scope, to prevent it to veer too far off from the subject.
